CVE ID :CVE-2026-59237

Published : July 16, 2026, 2:35 p.m. | 49 minutes ago

Description :Authorization Bypass Through User-Controlled Key (CWE-639) in the Order and OrderItem REST API controllers in Roskus Prospero Flow CRM before 5.5.3 allows a remote, authenticated user to read, modify, and delete orders and order items belonging to any other company (tenant) via a sequential numeric {id}
